  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of that register is to collect medical information about patients suffering of
      APS with or without associated SLE.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Recruitment of patients with APS and SLE treated. Retrospective and prospective register.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
